data.description: Remodeled and updated between 2018-2020. Beautifully remodeled 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath cottage in the heart of Bay Minette. You do NOT want to miss these fantastic updates! (2018) Turn-key ready with two brand new HVAC units (inside and out), new master bathroom shower, brand new kitchen cabinets and granite, light fixtures, new Samsung stainless steel appliances, new deck, new flooring, fresh paint inside and out…the list goes on and on! This home has PLENTY of room to spread out with an additional 19.5 x 15 foot family room. Two bathrooms downstairs (including the master) and two very large (13 x 14 and 15 x 14) bedrooms upstairs. New architectural shingle roof (2020). This is a MUST SEE! Shows beautifully!
